      MaskType		      "Block Processing"
      MaskDescription	      "Repeats a user-specified operation on submatrices of the input matrix.\n\nThis block extr"
      "acts submatrices of a user-specified size from the input matrix. It sends each submatrix to a subsystem for proc"
      "essing, and then reassembles each subsystem output into the output matrix.\n\nUse the Block size and Overlap par"
      "ameters to specify the size and overlap of each submatrix in cell array format."
      MaskHelp		      "eval('helpview(fullfile(docroot,''toolbox'',''vipblks'',''vipblks.map''),''vipblockprocessing''"
      ")');"
      MaskPromptString	      "Number of inputs:|Number of outputs:|Block size:|Overlap size:|Order of traversing:"
